---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="White Paper - ECOH">
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>ECOH White Paper</h1>
      <h2>Employee and Community Ownership in Australia</h2>
      <p class="release-date">Expected Release: May 2026</p>

      <p>
        We are developing a comprehensive white paper that captures insights and learnings from our
        2025 Community of Practice sessions. This advocacy paper makes the case for employee and
        community ownership as underutilised tools for business succession and worker wealth-building
        in Australia.
      </p>

      <aside class="callout">
        <h4>Pre-release summary now available</h4>
        <p>
          Ahead of the full release, we've published a pre-release executive summary together with
          selected excerpts from the forthcoming paper.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="https://public-pc.s3.amazonaws.com/Employee_and_Community_Ownership_in_Australia_Pre-release_Summary_2026-04-19.pdf"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="callout-link"
          >
            Read the pre-release summary (PDF) →
          </a>
        </p>
      </aside>

      <h3>The white paper will cover:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Australia's ownership opportunity</strong> — the succession challenge and why ownership
          structure matters
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>What works</strong> — practical models including EOTs, worker cooperatives, and
          community ownership structures
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Australian voices</strong> — case studies and insights from practitioners across the
          country
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Barriers holding Australia back</strong> — regulatory, tax, and knowledge gaps
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>International lessons</strong> — what other countries are doing (UK, US, Canada, Denmark)
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>The path forward</strong> — concrete recommendations for government, advisors, and
          business owners
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        The paper is authored by practitioners, researchers, and advocates who have participated in
        ECOH sessions. It presents substantial evidence while acknowledging we are not neutral
        observers — we want to see more employee and community-owned businesses in Australia, and we
        want government policy to make that easier.
      </p>

      <p>
        We welcome your interest in this work. If you'd like to stay informed about the white paper's
        release or contribute insights, please get in touch.
      </p>

      <aside class="callout">
        <h4>Launch event recording</h4>
        <p>
          The white paper was launched at The Kelvin Club in Melbourne on 21 April 2026. A recording
          of the event is available on YouTube.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://youtu.be/Q8u_fkZKxLo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="callout-link">
            Watch the launch event on YouTube →
          </a>
        </p>
      </aside>

      <div class="launch-photos">
        <figure class="landscape">
          <img src="/images/launch/ecoh-launch-1.jpg" alt="ECOH white paper launch event at The Kelvin Club, Melbourne" loading="lazy" width="1000" height="667" />
        </figure>
        <figure class="portrait">
          <img src="/images/launch/ecoh-launch-2.jpg" alt="ECOH white paper launch event at The Kelvin Club, Melbourne" loading="lazy" width="667" height="1000" />
        </figure>
      </div>
      <p class="photo-credit">Photos from the launch event, 21 April 2026. Photo credit: Eric Algra.</p>

      <aside class="callout">
        <h4>Further viewing: Graeme Nuttall on employee ownership</h4>
        <p>
          An earlier presentation from Graeme Nuttall, a leading international voice on employee
          ownership trusts.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://youtu.be/hlQ-hCWJHag" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="callout-link">
            Watch on YouTube →
          </a>
        </p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #2563eb;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .release-date {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .callout {
    background: #eff6ff;
    border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .callout h4 {
    color: #2563eb;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .callout p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .callout p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .callout-link {
    color: #2563eb;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .callout-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .launch-photos {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .launch-photos figure {
    margin: 0;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .launch-photos figure.landscape {
    flex: 1.499 1 0;
  }

  .launch-photos figure.portrait {
    flex: 0.667 1 0;
  }

  .launch-photos img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .launch-photos figure.landscape,
    .launch-photos figure.portrait {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
    }
  }

  .photo-credit {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
